plays.text: Jumpball: Janell Burse vs. Michelle Snow. Tina Thompson gains possession.
Betty Lennox Shooting Foul. Sheryl Swoopes gains possession.
Sheryl Swoopes made Free Throw 1 of 2.
Sheryl Swoopes missed Free Throw 2 of 2.
Sue Bird made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Tiffani Johnson.
Tina Thompson made 14 ft Two Point Shot. Assisted by Dawn Staley.
Tina Thompson missed 23 ft Three Point Jumper.
Roneeka Hodges's Layup blocked by Janell Burse.
Betty Lennox missed 12 ft Running Jumper.
Roneeka Hodges made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Dawn Staley.
